data.description: Like new, beautifully maintained single-story home in Mission Del Lago.  This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a great open concept floorplan that's perfect for entertaining! The master bedroom is split from the secondary bedrooms for added privacy and includes a full bath and room walk-in closet. Enjoy BBQ's and relaxation in the low maintenance backyard.  Very popular location that's a short distance to local schools, entertainment, restaurants, shopping, and more. Seller willing to contribute 4,500.00 towards closing costs!!! Schedule your tour today!!!
